    h3 Per le compagnie
    p.text Penso questo paragrafo sia piuttosto inutile perché le compagnie sono per la maggior parte al di fuori dell'Italia, ma per far capire la visione d’insieme:
    .tableContainer
        div.col-md-12.tableborder
            span.col-md-5.lighter
                p
                    b Sii trasparente
            span.col-md-1
            span.col-md-6.lighter
                p Do complete transparency report, fight against the gag order, do internal awareness on data usage, disclose your minimization policy or we assume you have not. Disclosure of the meta-data collected and the third parties you sell the data. The tracking business is surveillance.

            span.col-md-5.lighter
                p
                    b Allow pseudonymous access
            span.col-md-1
            span.col-md-6.lighter
                p Give your users the freedom to access your service pseudonymously. Real-name policies and their ilk are especially harmful to vulnerable populations, including pro-democracy activists and the LGBT community. For bonus points, don't restrict access to logged-in users.

            span.col-md-5.lighter
                p
                    b Stop behavioral analysis
            span.col-md-1
            span.col-md-6.lighter
                p Do not attempt to use your data to make decisions about user preferences and characteristics—like political preference or sexual orientation—that users did not explicitly specify themselves. Let users modify data that's been collected about them so far, and giving them the option not to have your service collect this information about them at all.


